These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, pink, mauve, purple, yellow, lavender, aquamarine
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, blues, d&b, r&b, folk, hip-hop, classical
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes purple is not the fan hip-hop##6
 3. the fan indie is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the fan classical is somewhere to the right of the fan folk##5
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 6. the fan indie is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the fan blues##7
 8. the fan blues is on the left of the fan classical##1
 9. the fan r&b is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the fan d&b##7
10. the fan d&b is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
11. the fan folk is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
13. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
14. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
15. the person who likes yellow is the fan blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Color          | mauve    | turquise    | pink | lavender | purple | yellow    | aquamarine |
| Music-Genre   | folk | indie | d&b  | hip-hop   | r&b    | blues | classical |

