.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur, coach, dancer, librarian, pilot, musician
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, oliveros, dannemann, old-henry, ritmeester, davidoff, aristoff
 1. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere between the musician and the entrepreneur##7
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the dancer##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the pilot##1
 5. the accountant is somewhere between the old-henry-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##7
 6. the pilot is somewhere between the dancer and the dannemann-smoker##7
 7. the librarian is somewhere between the dancer and the entrepreneur##7
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
10. the librarian is somewhere to the right of the davidoff-smoker##5
11. the davidoff-smoker is not the musician##6
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
13. the ritmeester-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Job    | musician  | coach | pilot | dancer | accountant     | librarian | entrepreneur  |
| Cigar   | dannemann | davidoff | oliveros  | aristoff  | ritmeester | old-henry      | fonseca |

