.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: yellow, amber, black, ivory, blue, grey, mauve
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, action, crime, mystery, fantasy, disaster, documentary
 1. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who likes black and the person watching crime movies##2
 2. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 3. the person watching action movies is not the person who likes ivory##6
 4. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 5. the person watching western movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes blue##2
 6. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 7. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 9. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
10. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
11. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes blue is not the person watching western movies##6
13. the person who likes grey is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the person who likes blue##7
14. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
15. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
16. the person who likes blue is not the person watching disaster movies##6
17. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
18. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
19. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Color         | yellow | amber | grey | blue  | black | ivory | mauve |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | disaster       | western   | fantasy | mystery           | documentary     | crime     |

