.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, dunhill, mouseing, montecristo, pall-mall, old-henry
7 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, turtle, mouse, lizard, rabbit, goldfish
 1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 2. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
 3. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 4. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 5. the mouseing-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
 6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the lizard##7
 8. the mouseing-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
10. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
11. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the blend-smoker##7
12. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the old-henry-smoker##5
13. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
14. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
15. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
16. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
17. the owner of the mouse is between the pall-mall-smoker and the owner of the rabbit##2
18. the montecristo-smoker is not the owner of the goldfish##6
19. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2    |     3     |     4      |     5      |    6    |    7     |
