 1. the person eating eggplant is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 4. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the person eating apple and the person eating eggplant##7
 5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person eating artichoke##6
 9. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
10. the person who's hobby is reading is not the person eating artichoke##6
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
12. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
13. the person eating eggplant is not the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##6
14. the person eating mango is the person who's hobby is reading##1
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
16. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
17. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3

