16. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
17. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is cycling##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Sport           | handball | golf | sailing   | cycling | water-polo | parkour | surfing |
| Color   | amber     | apricot       | purple | lilac       | emerald   | orange | coral  |

