13. the musician is on the far left##1
14. the person who's birthday is in january is the coach##1
15. the fisherman is in an odd position##4
16. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
17. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
